title: Daily Wire Backstage: The Red Wave
description:
Watch the member block portion of the show exclusively on DailyWire+: https://get.dailywire.com/subscribe/plus

Will our famous art ever be safe from soup-throwing climate activists? What do the guys think of Jordan Peterson’s advice on marriage? Does anyone know what’s growing out the back of John Fetterman’s neck?

Join our special Midterms discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Michael Knowles, Matt Walsh, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing to find out!

Watch Election Wire for up-to-date coverage on the races and issues that will decide the balance of power in Washington: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-rJXsoWS5Do
